of	1
little	1
Larks	1
who	1
lived	1
with	1
their	1
mother	1
in	1
a	1
nest	1
in	1
a	1
cornfield.	1
When	1
the	1
corn	1
was	1
ripe	1
the	1
mother	1
Lark	1
watched	1
very	1
carefully	1
to	1
see	1
if	1
there	1
were	1
any	1
