things	1
get	1
done.	1
I	1
will	1
move	1
you	1
out	1
to-night."	1
A	1
TRUE	1
STORY	1
ABOUT	1
A	1
GIRL	1
Once	1
there	1
were	1
four	1
little	1
girls	1
who	1
lived	1
in	1
a	1
big,	1
bare	1
house,	1
in	1
