the	1
water.	1
When	1
he	1
began	1
to	1
swim	1
he	1
swam	1
out	1
to	1
where	1
the	1
river	1
was	1
the	1
very	1
deepest.	1
There	1
he	1
stopped,	1
and	1
said,--	1
"Oh,	1
Jackal!"	1
"Yes,"	1
said	1
the	1
little	1
Jackal.	1
"I	1
have	1
the	1
strangest	1
