the	1
tiny	1
shoots	1
and	1
leaves	1
to	1
the	1
ground.	1
More	1
came,	1
and	1
more,	1
and	1
ever	1
more,	1
and	1
as	1
they	1
came	1
they	1
spread	1
out	1
till	1
they	1
covered	1
a	1
