knelt	1
to	1
pray.	1
Others	1
gathered	1
round	1
and	1
joined	1
them,	1
weeping.	1
More	1
left	1
their	1
useless	1
struggles	1
and	1
knelt	1
beside	1
their	1
neighbours.	1
At	1
last	1
nearly	1
all	1
the	1
people	1
were	1
kneeling	1
on	1
the	1
desolate	1
fields	1
praying	1
for	1
deliverance	1
from	1
the	1
